data.title: Grizzlies' Zach Randolph: Leads team with 20 points in Game 3 loss
data.meta_description: tallied 20 points (9-21 FG, 2-2 FT), 11 rebounds and an assist over 39 minutes in Friday's 96-87 Game 3 loss to the Spurs. The veteran forward managed his second consecutive double-double, and enjoyed his best shooting night from the field during the series.
